text.content: Create a new refuel log when ever you refuel. Add a photo of the receipt to the page for logging if necessary as this will also be a good backup. Input name, cost for fuel only and litres you put in from pump as well as octane chosen (all from receipt). Put in the previous items odometer (untilI can automate that) and the current reading before leaving the pump. The number of km, L/100 economy and $/L will all be calculated automatically.

text.content: This log is to collect any cost associated with your car that is not fuel. A place to dump invoices, dates, mileage at time and to calculate actual costs after a period of time rather than theoretical.
